EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Contact.FirstName} {!Contact.LastName},
Go here to unsubscribe from all emails from our organization. https://{!jrsl_ul_Unsubscribe_Link__mdt.jrsl_ul_Site_Domain__c}/Unsubscribe?recordId={!Contact.Id}&Email={!Contact.Email}
Instructions: Change "our organization" to the name of your organization. Make sure you modify the text only version as well. Delete the instructions here and add the rest of your email above the link. Notes: This email template comes with the unmanaged package "Unsubscribe Link." The link will launch the Unsubscribe Link flow. The flow will have an error if an email address includes a special character like +. The package contains a visualforce email template that accommodates special characters. Better yet, use lightning templates and the Unsubscribe Link formula fields.
